      "duration": 2.29,
      "size": 36720,
      "text": "我们常说，当 x 趋近 a 时，f(x) 趋近极限 L。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "epsilon-delta",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-2",
      "filename": "intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/epsilon-delta/yunxi/intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.74,
      "size": 27792,
      "text": "可是趋近到底是什么意思？多近才算近？"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "epsilon-delta",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-3",
      "filename": "intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/epsilon-delta/yunxi/intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.28,
      "size": 36432,
      "text": "数学家用一对希腊字母 ε 和 δ，把这句直觉说得一清二楚。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "epsilon-delta",
      "section_id": "challenge",
      "line_id": "chal-1",
      "filename": "challenge-chal-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/epsilon-delta/yunxi/challenge-chal-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.86,
      "size": 29808,
      "text": "先由一个挑战者出场，他给出一个很小的正数 ε。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "epsilon-delta",
      "section_id": "challenge",
      "line_id": "chal-2",
      "filename": "challenge-chal-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/epsilon-delta/yunxi/challenge-chal-2.mp3",
      "duration": 3.01,
      "size": 48096,
      "text": "ε 划出一条水平带，要求 f(x) 必须落在 L 上下不超过 ε 的范围内。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "epsilon-delta",
      "section_id": "challenge",
      "line_id": "chal-3",
      "filename": "challenge-chal-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/epsilon-delta/yunxi/challenge-chal-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.87,
      "size": 29952,
      "text": "ε 越小，这条水平带越窄，要求就越苛刻。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "epsilon-delta",
      "section_id": "response",
      "line_id": "resp-1",
      "filename": "response-resp-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/epsilon-delta/yunxi/response-resp-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.59,
      "size": 41472,
      "text": "我们的回应是找出一个 δ，划出一条竖直带，宽度是 a 左右各 δ。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "epsilon-delta",
      "section_id": "response",
      "line_id": "resp-2",
      "filename": "response-resp-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/epsilon-delta/yunxi/response-resp-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.37,
      "size": 37872,
      "text": "只要 x 落在这条竖直带内，f(x) 就一定落在那条水平带内。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "epsilon-delta",
      "section_id": "response",
      "line_id": "resp-3",
      "filename": "response-resp-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/epsilon-delta/yunxi/response-resp-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.23,
      "size": 35712,
      "text": "图中绿色虚框，正是竖直带与水平带交出的安全区。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "epsilon-delta",
      "section_id": "forall",
      "line_id": "all-1",
      "filename": "forall-all-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/epsilon-delta/yunxi/forall-all-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.34,
      "size": 37440,
      "text": "关键在于，无论挑战者把 ε 压得多小，我们都能拿出对应的 δ。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "epsilon-delta",
      "section_id": "forall",
      "line_id": "all-2",
      "filename": "forall-all-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/epsilon-delta/yunxi/forall-all-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.26,
      "size": 36144,
      "text": "这个对任意 ε 都成立的承诺，才是极限等于 L 的真正含义。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "epsilon-delta",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-1",
